    "Mi mette a disagio."

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4487
translate it a3_emi_storage_space_9c299960:

    # "I continue to work my way inside her, working slowly and listening carefully to Emi's breathing."
    "Continuo a introdurmi dentro di lei, procedendo lentamente e ascoltando attentamente il respiro di Emi."

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4493
translate it a3_emi_storage_space_cec3713a:

    # "I reach my limit and pause. Emi looks back again, biting her lower lip."
    "Arrivo al limite e mi fermo. Emi torna a guardare indietro, mordendosi il labbro inferiore."

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4495
translate it a3_emi_storage_space_125b633f:

    # emi "Are you going to try moving, or are we just going to sit here feeling silly?"
    emi "Hai intenzione di provare a muoverti, o dobbiamo solo stare qui a sentirci stupidi?"

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4500
translate it a3_emi_storage_space_6fbc4ad0:

    # hi "No, I just wanted to give you a chance to adjust."
    hi "No, volevo solo darti la possibilità di adattarti."

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4502
translate it a3_emi_storage_space_865fa7d2:

    # "This doesn't make any sense."
    "Questo non ha senso."

# game/script-a3-emi.rpy:4504
translate it a3_emi_storage_space_f55892b0:

